header.gameNote: LITTLE CAESARS HORIZON LEAGUE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: Northern Kentucky swings the ball around, eventually finding Jordan Garnett who attacks and lays it in.
videos.headline: Good ball movement sets up a nifty finish for Northern Kentucky

videos.description: Northern Kentucky's Carson Williams rejects a shot, then throws the ball off of Jeremy Johnson to give possession to Northern Kentucky.
videos.headline: Heads up play from Williams gives Northern Kentucky the ball

videos.description: Milwaukee's Brett Prahl tips in a missed shot to beat the first half buzzer and sends Milwaukee into the locker room trailing by three.
videos.headline: Prahl's tip in beats the first half buzzer

videos.description: Northern Kentucky shares the ball around the perimeter, giving to Drew McDonald who hits a straight away 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McDonald buries a 3-pointer for Northern Kentucky

videos.description: Off a nice pass from August Haas, Bryce Nze powers in a dunk.
videos.headline: Nze powers in dunk for Milwaukee

videos.description: Milwaukee's August Haas drives then dishes to Cody Wichmann who buries a huge 3-pointer for the Panthers.
videos.headline: Wichmann hits crucial 3-pointer for Milwaukee

videos.description: Northern Kentucky defeats Milwaukee 59-53 in the Horizon League Championship.
videos.headline: Northern Kentucky punches its ticket to the NCAA Tournament

videos.description: Postgame breakdown of Northern Kentucky's Horizon League Championship victory.
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown of Northern Kentucky's Horizon League Championship victory
